➜ Shoe Sales EDA Project

➜ Project Overview
Performed Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a shoe sales dataset using Python.

➜ Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib

➜ Analysis Performed
- Data Cleaning
- Missing Value Check
- Duplicate Detection
- Univariate Analysis
- Bivariate Analysis
- Correlation Analysis
- Outlier Detection

➜ Dataset Features
- Brand
- Country
- Revenue
- Units Sold
- Price
- Sales Channel

➜ Conclusion
The project analyzed sales patterns, revenue trends, and relationships between different variables.
